data.description: Welcome home! This home features 3-bedrooms, 1-bath  with a bonus room doubling as a 4th bedroom. Enjoy 1,252 sq ft of single-floor living, complemented by a detached 672 sq ft garage. The covered patio and private backyard is perfect for relaxation. Brand new roof was installed in 2023! Conveniently located for an easy commute to Fort Campbell, Clarksville, I24, or Hopkinsville. Come make this your home! Schedule your showing today!
